title: Allstar BIO21712 Bumpits Hair Volumizing Inserts- Dark Brown/Black
description: The Bumpits Hair Volumizing Leave-In Inserts give you instant volume and let you enjoy feeling confident and beautiful, like you stepped out of a professional salon. Not only does this Set of 3 Bumpits give you additional volume in your hair, it will give you an entirely new look whether you are out dancing, working out, going to work, shopping, or at a formal event. The raised patented edging firmly grips any hair type. For those ladies with finer, thinner hair, you can do some light teasing at the base to ensure a firm hold. Included are three dark brown/black Bumpits in small, medium and large along with a teasing comb and styling guide.
